{"tid":927965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國防自主】強化實力 印度海軍：首艘自製航母維克蘭特號將於2020年服役","createTime":"2018-12-04T13:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T14:47:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"35eac0220eadcdd245cafa9566da087deed733cf","tid":927965,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20181204210053594328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20181204210053594328.jpg&h=c2fc1098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度首艘國產航空母艦維克蘭特號。（圖片取自印度海軍）<br />\n<br />\n為鞏固在南亞霸權、印度近年來不斷砸重金採購與升級軍備，除了讓國際軍火大廠垂涎三尺的鉅額戰機訂單，海軍的航空母艦和潛艦升級也是一大亮點。<br />\n而目前與俄羅斯一樣、僅有一艘現役航母的印度，10月也傳出好消息，經過5個月的升級改造工程，超日王號航空母艦（INS Vikarmaditya）已出廠進行海試，很快就能回到任務內。<br />\n<br />\n首艘國產航母將於2020年服役<br />\n 印度《經濟時報》（Economic Times）報導，印度東部海軍司令部司令、辛格中將（Karambir Singh）4日在海軍日上宣布，首艘國產自製航空母艦（IAC-1）維克蘭特號（INS Vikrant），將於2020年加入海軍服役，目前艦載機仍暫由米格29K（MiG-29）中隊擔任，並由東部海軍司令部管轄。<br />\n辛格中將表示，「為維持印度的海上利益，我軍需要至少兩艘現役航空母艦。現役的超日王號、以及兩艘國產航母的加入，就是為了讓將來能確保，至少有兩個航母打擊群可協同運作。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20181025192409470540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20181025192409470540.jpg&h=112a18b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度唯一現役的航空母艦「超日王號」。（圖片取自印度海軍）<br />\n<br />\n不過，雖然一號艦服役時間已定，當被問及二號艦維沙爾號（INS Vishal）時，辛格中將表示，二號艦目前在籌備階段，海軍將持續商議艦上系統配備再做打算。<br />\n<br />\n從2009年開始興建、至今仍未完成的國產航母<br />\n從2009年開始動工、由科欽造船廠負責興建的維克蘭特號航空母艦，其名之意是「我能擊敗那些與我對抗的人」，以此紀念獨立後印度第一艘航母、原英國皇家海軍的威嚴級航空母艦赫丘利斯號（HMS Hercules）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/INS_Vikrant_(R11)_with_a_Sea_King_helicopter_during_Indo-Pakistani_war_of_1971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2FINS_Vikrant_%28R11%29_with_a_Sea_King_helicopter_during_Indo-Pakistani_war_of_1971.jpg&h=2e3e7607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n退役多年、印度首艘航空母艦維克蘭特號（R11）與海王直升機。（圖片取自印度海軍）<br />\n <br />\n公開資料顯示，維克蘭特號擁有4萬噸排水量、船身全長262公尺，擁有4座通用電氣LM2500燃氣渦輪發動機，最大航程可達1萬5000公里。巡航最高時速可達52公里、搭載約1400名船員，甲板上則能停靠14架米格29K戰機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/INS_Vikrant_being_undocked_at_the_Cochin_Shipyard_Limited_in_2015_(08).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2FINS_Vikrant_being_undocked_at_the_Cochin_Shipyard_Limited_in_2015_%2808%29.jpg&h=5f9dd4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n維克蘭特號航空母艦2015年6月出船塢。（圖片取自印度海軍）<br />\n <img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/INS_Vikrant_being_undocked_at_the_Cochin_Shipyard_Limited_in_2015_(07).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2FINS_Vikrant_being_undocked_at_the_Cochin_Shipyard_Limited_in_2015_%2807%29.jpg&h=80241b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2015年在科欽造船廠的維克蘭特級航空母艦。（圖片取自印度海軍）<br />\n <br />\n2013年8月、艦身工程完成度75%的維克蘭特號在造船廠內下水，但後續興建工程進度卻不如預期，本預定2018年底能投入服役，如今卻再度延期2年、經完整的海試和調整後再服役。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/PixA%20(copy)_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2FPixA%2520%28copy%29_0.jpg&h=4bf5c636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 仍在興建中的維克蘭特號航空母艦。（圖片取自印度海軍）<br />\n <br />\n下一代艦載機該由誰接棒？<br />\n除了航空母艦外，有意擴大自身海軍規模的印度，辛格中將也在記者會上透露，已有27艘軍艦和潛艇下訂、都將屬於「國艦國造」計畫的一部分。但對於印度海軍來說，還有另一個問題要考慮，那就艦載機的新選擇究竟是誰？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/123_43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2F123_43.jpg&h=97a9bda3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準備降落於超日王航母甲板的米格29K戰機。（圖片取自印度海軍）<br />\n國產的光輝（Tejas）海軍版已不符需求，當前的米格29K機隊又面臨妥善率不佳的困境，雖宣布對外採購66架新版本可用艦載機，但何時才能確定與購入，恐怕都影響著印度想重新擴張海上霸權的野心，也牽動著南亞次大陸的國際局勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=53459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D53459&d=B27wlD5JKmSEs0Pp72ptJBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=15955780\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=53459</a>"},{"pid":"5599de8d4e9347d01b62401efc24399440b4b488","tid":927965,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"兩大海上移動炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba29e4c689ab03f96e019bf163a58ec8e0eb6739","tid":927965,"uid":34949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:55:38.000Z","msg":"咖哩同支那邊個廢啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e7fc1d6dfec3c1ba8dca697c15f9063114fb07","tid":927965,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"辛格中將（Karambir Singh）<br />\n又係叫阿星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8e4f9265a1e7bab63c5ebecbe9ba69658cea69","tid":927965,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"開唔開到入恆河"},{"pid":"6ff244187479426fb127497517263d46801d64ca","tid":927965,"uid":37874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba29e4c689ab03f96e019bf163a58ec8e0eb6739","tid":927965,"uid":34949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:55:38.000Z","msg":"咖哩同支那邊個廢啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"客觀咁睇 淨係比較個船廠<br />\n大陸果個先進/新淨好多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0ca0a58d6027d902dd531cfe2f207a10ee6c7c","tid":927965,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9622fbe01200d48a945946b1da91210a2cd6d795","tid":927965,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:30:54.000Z","msg":"